<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM10.2.3">
<l>taṇṭa kāraṇi yampukun taṉṟu taiya laittaka viliyeṅ kōmāṉ</l>
<l>koṇṭu pōntukeṭ ṭāṉemak kiṅkōr kuṟṟa millaikol lēlkula vēntē</l>
<l>peṇṭi rālkeṭu mikkuṭi taṉṉaip pēcu kiṉṟateṉ tācara tīyuṉ</l>
<l>aṇṭa vāṇaru kappatē ceytā yañci ṉōmtaṭam poṅkattam poṅkō.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Entering the Daṇḍaka forest, then abducting [your] beauty,</l>
<l rend="indent">our merciless king was ruined.</l>
<l>There was no fault of ours here; do not slay us, royal king.</l>
<l>What’s [the use of] talking about this clan which was ruined by a woman?</l>
<l rend="indent">Dāśarathi,</l>
<l>You do what your followers who resort to you desire. We are frightened.</l>
<l rend="indent">Oh, it’s a turbulent road; it’s a turbulent path!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
